        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/03/2026-03-25-21-21-51-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:133339ec4a23cca01d4650504edc29d2b07bd6845395e4d5d2c27b2e82ce78eafe3c870388ac5bbe2636dd811ba389c7c7d9507bd280a6f9b0efef496d2ecd47"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/03/2026-03-25-21-21-51-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
